description: Style of the content in each page and flow
alwaysApply: true
---
- Content should follow TDD flows with Red, Green, and then Refactor.
- All content pages should be setup with the same basic structure, including styles of titles, use of icons and flow.  
- Green phase should be hidden by default with a button to show 
- All code in content pages should be in a code block with a copy button
- All green phases should be hidden by default with a show button to unhide it.
- All pages should include setup instructions for the content including folder structures and empty files. 
- All code blocks should specify the subpath to the file (example: hello-World/hello-world.py)

